title: TF 1.3 with AMD ROCm build error on ARM64 Ubuntu 16.04
body_html:
I meet error at ARM64 ubuntu 16.04 with AMD ROCm and TF 1.3 https://github.com/ROCmSoftwarePlatform/tensorflow
